[11.231992, "o", "The agent will hypothesize a change, implement it, test, benchmark,\r\nand decide whether to keep or discard.\r\n\r\n"]
[11.233653, "o", "$ ddx agent run --text \"You are running one experiment iteration to optimize src/process.js.\r\n\r\nGoal: redu...\"\r\n\r\n"]
[33.582647, "o", "Perfect! Here's the optimization report:\r\n\r\n## Change Made\r\n**Replaced string concatenation with array join pattern** (lines 5-9)\r\n- Before: `result = result + item[j].toUpperCase()` (quadratic string rebuild)\r\n- After: `chars.push(item[j].toUpperCase())` then `chars.join('')` (linear array operations)\r\n\r\n## Results\r\n- **Baseline metric:** 241.1ms\r\n- **New metric:** 109.6ms\r\n- **Improvement:** 54.6% faster вњ…\r\n- **Tests:** All 4 tests pass вњ…\r\n\r\n## Decision\r\n**KEEP** вЂ” This is a significant performance improvement with no functionality impact. The change eliminates the O(nВІ) string concatenation bottleneck in the inner loop.\r\n\r\n"]
[36.584559, "o", "After iteration 1:\r\n$ npm test\r\n"]
[37.203512, "o", "\r\n> perf-lab@1.0.0 test\r\n> node --test\r\n\r\n"]
