[42.775932, "o", "\r\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\r\n  ACT 3: Experiment вЂ” Iteration 2\r\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\r\n\r\n"]
[44.779858, "o", "$ ddx agent run --text \"Continue optimizing src/process.js. This is iteration 2.\r\n\r\nRead the current src/p...\"\r\n\r\n"]
[68.226465, "o", "## Iteration 2 Results\r\n\r\n**Change Made:** Replaced O(n) `indexOf()` duplicate checking with O(1) Set-based tracking\r\n\r\n**Metric:** `runtime=88.3ms`\r\n\r\n**Code Change:**\r\n- Added `const seen = new Set()` to track seen results\r\n- Changed `results.indexOf(result) === -1` to `!seen.has(result)`\r\n- Add to Set before pushing to results array\r\n\r\n**Analysis:**\r\n- вњ… Tests pass (4/4)\r\n- This optimizes duplicate detection from O(n) per item to O(1)\r\n- Overall complexity improved from O(nВІ) to O(nГ—m) where n=items, m=max string length\r\n- The Set lookup is dramatically faster than indexOf for larger datasets\r\n\r\n**Recommendation:** вњ… **KEEP**\r\n\r\nThis is a fundamental algorithmic improvement that will scale well as the input size grows. The Set provides constant-time duplicate checking vs. linear scanning through the results array.\r\n\r\n"]
[71.229152, "o", "After iteration 2:\r\n$ npm test\r\n"]
[72.182912, "o", "\r\n> perf-lab@1.0.0 test\r\n> node --test\r\n\r\n"]
[72.688942, "o", "в–¶ processStrings\r\n  \u001b[32mвњ” uppercases all items \u001b[90m(2.486406ms)\u001b[39m\u001b[39m\r\n"]
[72.699431, "o", "  \u001b[32mвњ” deduplicates results \u001b[90m(0.401248ms)\u001b[39m\u001b[39m\r\n  \u001b[32mвњ” handles empty input \u001b[90m(0.520405ms)\u001b[39m\u001b[39m\r\n  \u001b[32mвњ” handles single character strings \u001b[90m(0.253264ms)\u001b[39m\u001b[39m\r\n\u001b[32mв–¶ \u001b[39mprocessStrings \u001b[90m(8.892661ms)\u001b[39m\r\n\r\n"]
