[88.051306, "o", "What you just saw:\r\n"]
[88.051719, "o", "  1. A deliberately slow function with correctness tests\r\n  2. Baseline measurement establishing the starting metric\r\n  3. Two experiment iterations: hypothesize в†’ edit в†’ test в†’ benchmark в†’ keep/discard\r\n  4. Final result: faster code with all tests still passing\r\n\r\nhelix experiment enforces: tests MUST pass. If they don't,\r\nthe change is discarded regardless of metric improvement.\r\nCorrectness is non-negotiable.\r\n\r\n"]
